Dear Sir or Madam:\\[1.5em]
%
I am writing to apply to the open adjunct faculty position in Economics at Grand View University. I am a current second year PhD student at Iowa State, where I was initially accepted as a Masters student where due to strong performance in the  class room I was accepted into the PhD program before finishing my Masters thesis. Despite this, I have continued to work on research, and have coauthored a paper with two faculty, and plan to defend a Masters thesis during the Summer of 2015 even though it is not required by the usual Doctorate program of study.

In accordance with my strong personal drive, I have had two professors give me strong amounts of personal autonomy during their classes. 
               
